(g) provide for the status of national and representative groups;
provide for the status of national and representative groups;
(h) prescribe the manner and form in which application for the award of national artistic honours shall be made; and
prescribe the manner and form in which application for the award of national artistic honours shall be made; and
(i) provide for the procedure for becoming an associate body of the Council .
