(1) The Council shall consist of— (a) two members appointed by the Minister; (b) the Director of Cultural Services; (c) one member to be appointed by each registered body; and (d) one member appointed by the Ministry responsible for— (i) education; (ii) information and broadcasting; (iii) science, technology and vocational training; and (iv) tourism.
